		"description": {
			"chat": "",
			"unidentified": "",
			"value": "\n      <div topic='Robe of Blending' level='8'><p><b>Robe of Blending:</b> When this robe is put on, the wearer intuitively knows that the garment has very special properties. A <i>robe of blending</i> enables its wearer to appear to be part of his surroundings. This allows him a +10 competence bonus on Hide checks. The wearer can adopt the appearance of another creature, as with the <i>disguise self</i> spell, at will. All creatures acquainted with and friendly to the wearer see him normally.</p><p>Moderate illusion; CL 10th; Craft Wondrous Item, <i>disguise self</i>; Price 30,000 gp; Weight 1 lb.</p>\n</div>\n    "
